<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #57B9FF;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px;
    }
    .features {
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .feature {
      margin: 15px 0;
      padding: 10px;
      background: #f9f9f9;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
    .cta-button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background-color: #57B9FF;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #666;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1><%= storeName %></h1>
    <p>Welcome to Our Community!</p>
  </div>
  
  <div class="content">
    <p>Dear <%= user.name %>,</p>
    
    <p>Welcome to <%= storeName %>! We're thrilled to have you join our community of educational toy enthusiasts. Your account has been successfully created, and you're now ready to explore our world of learning and fun.</p>
    
